Description: Companion Shiny app that support the surveydown survey platform. The default method for working with a surveydown survey is to edit the plain text survey.qmd and app.R files. With sdstudio, you can create, preview and manage surveys with a Graphical User Interface.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://sdstudio.surveydown.org
